OL,3,CPolitician calls for urgent action
OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,FThe runway could not therefore safely
OL,7,Freopen, and an emergency assessment
OL,8,Fwas conducted by a pavement specialist
OL,9,Fon Saturday afternoon (1 February).
OL,11,FThe decision was made to keep the
OL,12,Frunway closed until Sunday morning
OL,13,Fearliest (2 February).
OL,15,FSteve Roberts, one of Alderney's
OL,16,Fpoliticians, says this latest problem
OL,17,Fhighlights the need for the States of
OL,18,FGuernsey to approve immediate funding
OL,19,Ffor the runway's repairs to be
OL,20,Fundertaken.
