OL,3,CPolitician calls for urgent action
OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,7,FCommittee scrapped their plans to
OL,8,Fextend the landing strip and build a
OL,9,Fnew terminal in Alderney after costs
OL,10,Frose from an estimated #12.2 million
OL,11,Fto #37 million last summer.
OL,13,FBut Alderney residents say action is
OL,14,Fneeded.
OL,16,FAlderney Represenative Steve Roberts
OL,17,Fsays: "The runway refurbishment must
OL,18,Fbe brought forward as soon as
OL,19,Fpossible. It needs upgrading, not
OL,20,Fpatching, which is costing a fortune
OL,21,Fanyway.
