OL,3,CPolitician calls for urgent action
OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,F"It really is a lifeline to two
OL,7,Fthousand Bailiwick taxpayers."
OL,9,FThis weekend's problems come after a
OL,10,Fvisit from the Civil Aviation
OL,11,FAuthority raised concerns that the
OL,12,Frunway might be forced to close
OL,13,Findefinitely if repairs are not
OL,14,Fprioritised.
OL,16,FThis would leave the island's 2,100
OL,17,Fresidents dependent on a ferry service
OL,18,F- plus potentially helicopters for
OL,19,Fmedivacs.
