OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,FMr Roberts says this prospect would be
OL,7,F"catastrophic" from a medical
OL,8,Fperspective, highlighting the
OL,9,Fdependency on air travel of islanders
OL,10,Fwho are accessing treatments in
OL,11,FGuernsey or Southampton.
OL,13,FHe adds: "Boats are being used, but to
OL,14,Fask the sick, elderly, and disabled to
OL,15,Fembark and disembark using a ladder at
OL,16,Fthe Harbour is inadequate.
OL,18,F"They are totally reliant on our
OL,19,Frunway being serviceable."
